# Defense-in-depth ignore rules for ripgrep/fd/editor search tools.
# Git already ignores these in .gitignore; this file prevents routine
# local scans from walking browser caches, cookies, sessions, screenshots,
# traces, and other runtime artifacts.

.local/
.local*/
**/.local/
**/.local*/

browser-profiles/
**/browser-profiles/
**/servicenow-browser-profiles/

screenshots/
**/screenshots/
logs/
**/logs/
private/
field-test-results/
field-test-notes/

*.har
*.trace.zip
*.webm
storage-state*.json
storageState.json
*.storageState.json
*.cookies.json
*.session.json
